name: Smallprint Magic Inkless Wipe Kits
description: Smallprints fantastic kit enables you to take a gorgeous impression of your child's hand or foot print, using our magic inkless wipes and specially coated paper - It's completely clean and mess free! These prints can then be framed and displayed as a beautiful reminder of those tiny toes and fingers. Each kit contains enough paper to take 2 handprints and 2 footprints. It's easy-to-use and safe for children of all ages, even newborns. There are some ideas of what to do with your prints in the pack! You can even scan your prints and send them to Smallprint to make items from Smallprint's fabulous range of jewellery.
